# Routes
# This file defines all application routes (Higher priority routes first)
# https://www.playframework.com/documentation/latest/ScalaRouting
# ~~~~

# ~~~~
# In any normal API I would retrieve the user Id securely, e.g. from an OAuth token
# or at-least in an encrypted header however for speed I have just put the user Id in the url
# ~~~~

GET       /example              io.panda.example.controllers.ExampleController.getExample
PATCH     /example              io.panda.example.controllers.ExampleController.addItem
DELETE    /example              io.panda.example.controllers.ExampleController.deleteFromExample
